lead_paragraph: The South Korean Olympic committee has blocked former Olympic swimming champion Park Tae-hwan from competing at this year's games in Rio de Janeiro even though he finished serving a doping suspension in March.

headline.print_headline: Park Tae-Hwan Blocked From Competing at Olympics in Rio
